{"tid":1132794,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"唔好再問人地點解笑你毒撚","createTime":"2019-04-30T14:25:51.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-30T14:38:31.000Z","uid":202885,"like":5,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"79f44c78f22fd8c2ba33c41eaa25c93d4afd012e","tid":1132794,"uid":202885,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-30T14:25:51.000Z","msg":"毒撚最忌並唔係有自信<br />\n係忌在<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">唔肯認清自己係毒撚</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n一方面又要介意自己畀人笑<br />\n但又從來唔會做任何改變<br />\n<br />\n同肥人一樣 下下怨世怨父母<br />\n其實講到尾 就係天生少人一份毅力<br />\n人地推胸操背嗰時 你就係屋企打J<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n頭髮唔執 衣著又毒 性格又差<br />\n連自己最基本嘅形象唔在意 點贏得尊重<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n要學會面對它、接受它、處理它、放下它<br />\n如果唔係做死一世毒撚啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e0db24955e6ae63175790d3c7e0b6ac037c81fa1","tid":1132794,"uid":217352,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-30T14:35:09.000Z","msg":"哦"},{"pid":"6397926e31af30935ce69f58afb667744161bd69","tid":1132794,"uid":43231,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-30T14:38:31.000Z","msg":"受教了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}